column2: I would feel a sense of loss if an intelligent system was unavailable and I could no longer use it.
column3: Intelligent systems help me to understand the world around me.

column6: I'm concerned that intelligent systems will collect too much personal information from me.

column12: Intelligent systems are difficult to navigate.
column13: I find intelligent systems easy to use.
column14: Truck driving should be left to humans rather being handled by a system.
column15: Deliveries of products to customers can only be done by humans.
column16: I would not use a self driving driverless car as my primary means of transportation.

column18: When sentencing persons convicted of crimes, automated systems should be used instead of human judges or juries.
column19: Automated education systems are more effective than human led classrooms.
column20: Music streaming applications have the ability to make music recommendations for me that I will enjoy.

column22: Social media feeds are useful for suggesting content that I would like
